reviewText: Inspector Gadget is a cross between that consumate Spy Maxwell Smart Control Agent 86 and that Great Criminologist Inspector Clouseau.  Gadget is a somewhat robotic if not even cybornetic being who is a spy of sorts.  He is at times smart, wise and very lucky.  He misses obvious clues only to pick up on subtle clues.  Gadget for all his faughts is one of the good guys who always manages to foil the best laid plans of enemies.  Gadget has a host of followers who help guide him toward successful outcomes.  While Gadget gets into similiar types of troube in most episodes you never get tired of watching.  Gadget himself has such a strong personality and screen pressence that he never gets old.  Gadget is the personification of boundless energies directed in the cause of good.  Gadget is never vulgar and never crude he is always fun and happy go lucky.  Even in adversity Gadget see's something funny something uplifting that helps him carry the day.  Gadget is an animated comedy created mainly for children but The Inspector Gadget Stories are never Childish!  Inspector gadget never insults the intelligence of his audiences young or old and for that reason I love my Inspector Gadget Mega Set and I am over 50 years old.As for the video and audio quality I find both good making the product extremely watchable.  I rate this product 5 stars because; they were earned not given!
summary: FOR ALL OF THOSE WHO ACHE TO GET THEIR GADGET ON - THIS IS THE INSPECTOR GADGET MEGA-SET FOR YOU!
